{"id":559721,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/【草泥马语】文贵伐赵/","date":"2017-05-24T14:42:35Z","modified":"2017-05-26T06:11:01Z","title":"【草泥马语】文贵伐赵","content":"<p>近日，随着郭文贵网络爆料内容的逐渐丰富，在越来越多的网民眼中，郭作为一个知晓内情者所揭示曝光的中共官员贪腐事实、体制黑幕，已经形成了一种对中共既得利益权贵（赵家）们的强大冲击力，于是以“荆轲刺秦“做比喻，创造出“文贵伐赵”一词，赞誉他在真相层面上动摇体制的作用，以及不甘沦为权斗牺牲品的个人勇气。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/twilightcn/status/856721001337442305\">https://twitter.com/twilightcn/status/856721001337442305</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/twilightcn/status/856015527470170112\">https://twitter.com/twilightcn/status/856015527470170112</a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-lang=\"en\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/KwokMiles\">@KwokMiles</a> 文贵伐赵，自身安危第一重要。</p>\n<p>&mdash; SimpleDeeb✊️✊️✊️ (@SimpleDeeb) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SimpleDeeb/status/867919824546021376\">May 26, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p> <script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-conversation=\"none\" data-lang=\"en\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/gaoyu200812\">@gaoyu200812</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/yangjianli001\">@yangjianli001</a> 文贵伐赵，全国发酵</p>\n<p>&mdash; Joye✊✊✊ (@Joye04346063) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Joye04346063/status/867904287355019264\">May 26, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p> <script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-lang=\"en\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">🎬文贵伐赵，一切都是刚刚开始。</p>\n<p>&mdash; zloading (@zloading) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/zloading/status/867680004942970880\">May 25, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p> <script async src=\"//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-558805\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/郭文贵2-720x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"512\" height=\"728\" srcset=\"https://chi